{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_d5da171b19554109809101c1","type":"tool_result","content":"1\t.. image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/dm/django-autocomplete-light.svg\n2\t   :target: https://pypi.python.org/pypi/django-autocomplete-light\n3\t.. image:: https://badge.fury.io/py/django-autocomplete-light.png\n4\t   :target: http://badge.fury.io/py/django-autocomplete-light\n5\t.. image:: https://secure.travis-ci.org/yourlabs/django-autocomplete-light.png?branch=master\n6\t    :target: http://travis-ci.org/yourlabs/django-autocomplete-light\n7\t.. image:: https://codecov.io/github/yourlabs/django-autocomplete-light/coverage.svg?branch=master\n8\t    :target: https://codecov.io/github/yourlabs/django-autocomplete-light?branch=master\n9\t\n10\tFeatures\n11\t--------\n12\t\n13\t- **Django 4.2 support starting DAL 3.10**, support for earlier Django versions\n14\t  in DAL < 3.10\n15\t- Django (multiple) choice support,\n16\t- Django (multiple) model choice support,\n17\t- Django generic foreign key support (through django-querysetsequence),\n18\t- Django generic many to many relation support (through django-generic-m2m and\n19\t  django-gm2m)\n20\t- Multiple widget support: select2.js, easy to add more.\n21\t- Creating choices that don't exist in the autocomplete,\n22\t- Offering choices that depend on other fields in the form, in an elegant and\n23\t  innovative way,\n24\t- Dynamic widget creation (ie. inlines), supports YOUR custom scripts too,\n25\t- Provides a test API for your awesome autocompletes, to support YOUR custom\n26\t  use cases too,\n27\t- A documented automatically tested example for each use case in test_project.\n28\t\n29\tResources\n30\t---------\n31\t\n32\t- `**Documentation** graciously hosted\n33\t  <http://django-autocomplete-light.rtfd.org>`_ by `RTFD\n34\t  <http://rtfd.org>`_\n35\t- `Mailing list graciously hosted\n36\t  <http://groups.google.com/group/yourlabs>`_ by `Google\n37\t  <http://groups.google.com>`_\n38\t- For **Security** issues, please contact security@<our github group name>.org\n39\t- `Git graciously hosted\n40\t  <https://github.com/yourlabs/django-autocomplete-light/>`_ by `GitHub\n41\t  <http://github.com>`_,\n42\t- `Package graciously hosted\n43\t  <http://pypi.python.org/pypi/django-autocomplete-light/>`_ by `PyPi\n44\t  <http://pypi.python.org/pypi>`_,\n45\t"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"92e63ed9-a118-4963-ab75-1247a9691865","uuid":"41eb507f-6fdc-49be-81e9-cfd33ba5c2e1","timestamp":"2026-04-06T20:40:44.738Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/workspace/README.rst","content":".. image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/dm/django-autocomplete-light.svg\n   :target: https://pypi.python.org/pypi/django-autocomplete-light\n.. image:: https://badge.fury.io/py/django-autocomplete-light.png\n   :target: http://badge.fury.io/py/django-autocomplete-light\n.. image:: https://secure.travis-ci.org/yourlabs/django-autocomplete-light.png?branch=master\n    :target: http://travis-ci.org/yourlabs/django-autocomplete-light\n.. image:: https://codecov.io/github/yourlabs/django-autocomplete-light/coverage.svg?branch=master\n    :target: https://codecov.io/github/yourlabs/django-autocomplete-light?branch=master\n\nFeatures\n--------\n\n- **Django 4.2 support starting DAL 3.10**, support for earlier Django versions\n  in DAL < 3.10\n- Django (multiple) choice support,\n- Django (multiple) model choice support,\n- Django generic foreign key support (through django-querysetsequence),\n- Django generic many to many relation support (through django-generic-m2m and\n  django-gm2m)\n- Multiple widget support: select2.js, easy to add more.\n- Creating choices that don't exist in the autocomplete,\n- Offering choices that depend on other fields in the form, in an elegant and\n  innovative way,\n- Dynamic widget creation (ie. inlines), supports YOUR custom scripts too,\n- Provides a test API for your awesome autocompletes, to support YOUR custom\n  use cases too,\n- A documented automatically tested example for each use case in test_project.\n\nResources\n---------\n\n- `**Documentation** graciously hosted\n  <http://django-autocomplete-light.rtfd.org>`_ by `RTFD\n  <http://rtfd.org>`_\n- `Mailing list graciously hosted\n  <http://groups.google.com/group/yourlabs>`_ by `Google\n  <http://groups.google.com>`_\n- For **Security** issues, please contact security@<our github group name>.org\n- `Git graciously hosted\n  <https://github.com/yourlabs/django-autocomplete-light/>`_ by `GitHub\n  <http://github.com>`_,\n- `Package graciously hosted\n  <http://pypi.python.org/pypi/django-autocomplete-light/>`_ by `PyPi\n  <http://pypi.python.org/pypi>`_,\n","numLines":45,"startLine":1,"totalLines":45}}}
