{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_10efff5dc1a34bb690daf732","type":"tool_result","content":"Web search results for query: \"django-generic-m2m pypi package\"\n\nThe user wants me to search for information about the \"django-generic-m2m\" PyPI package. This is a specific Python package that provides generic many-to-many relationships for Django. Let me search for this.\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"django-gm2m - PyPI\",\"url\":\"https://pypi.org/project/django-gm2m/\"},{\"title\":\"django-generic-m2m-field - PyPI\",\"url\":\"https://pypi.org/project/django-generic-m2m-field/\"},{\"title\":\"django-gm2m 0.4 - PyPI\",\"url\":\"https://pypi.org/project/django-gm2m/0.4/\"},{\"title\":\"gm2m-relations - PyPI\",\"url\":\"https://pypi.org/project/gm2m-relations/\"},{\"title\":\"coleifer/django-generic-m2m: relate anything to anything - GitHub\",\"url\":\"https://github.com/coleifer/django-generic-m2m\"},{\"title\":\"django-gm2m - PyPI\",\"url\":\"https://pypi.org/project/django-gm2m/0.1b1/\"},{\"title\":\"skip-django-generic-m2m-field - PyPI\",\"url\":\"https://pypi.org/project/skip-django-generic-m2m-field/\"},{\"title\":\"Generic M2M - Google Groups\",\"url\":\"https://groups.google.com/g/django-developers/c/Ygcb5xILAvI/m/K0PrmEc_EwAJ\"},{\"title\":\"django-generic-notifications - PyPI\",\"url\":\"https://pypi.org/project/django-generic-notifications/\"}]\n\nBased on the search results, there are a few related PyPI packages for Django generic many-to-many relationships:\n\n## Primary Package: **django-gm2m**\n- **PyPI URL**: https://pypi.org/project/django-gm2m/\n- **Description**: Django generic many-to-many field implementation that exposes a `GM2MField` combining features of the standard Django ManyToManyField\n- **Latest Version**: 0.4 (as shown in results)\n- **GitHub Repository**: https://github.com/coleifer/django-generic-m2m\n- **Purpose**: Allows you to create database-level relationships between various objects using a consistent API\n\n## Alternative Package: **django-generic-m2m-field**\n- **PyPI URL**: https://pypi.org/project/django-generic-m2m-field/\n- **Version**: 0.0.9\n\n## Related Package: **gm2m-relations**\n- **PyPI URL**: https://pypi.org/project/gm2m-relations/\n- **Description**: Implements Django REST Framework serializers to handle generic many-to-many relations\n- **Last Updated**: August 2023\n\nThe most established and commonly referenced package appears to be **django-gm2m** by coleifer, which has been around since at least 2014 and provides the core `GM2MField` implementation for relating any model to any other model in Django, similar to how Generic Foreign Keys work but for many-to-many relationships.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"92e63ed9-a118-4963-ab75-1247a9691865","uuid":"481aba79-245d-4afd-83aa-36930585ae69","timestamp":"2026-04-06T20:41:39.282Z","tool_use_result":{"query":"django-generic-m2m pypi package","results":["The user wants me to search for information about the \"django-generic-m2m\" PyPI package. This is a specific Python package that provides generic many-to-many relationships for Django. Let me search for this.",{"tool_use_id":"srvtoolu_774d861447f548d9a67a7f4b","content":[{"title":"django-gm2m - PyPI","url":"https://pypi.org/project/django-gm2m/"},{"title":"django-generic-m2m-field - PyPI","url":"https://pypi.org/project/django-generic-m2m-field/"},{"title":"django-gm2m 0.4 - PyPI","url":"https://pypi.org/project/django-gm2m/0.4/"},{"title":"gm2m-relations - PyPI","url":"https://pypi.org/project/gm2m-relations/"},{"title":"coleifer/django-generic-m2m: relate anything to anything - GitHub","url":"https://github.com/coleifer/django-generic-m2m"},{"title":"django-gm2m - PyPI","url":"https://pypi.org/project/django-gm2m/0.1b1/"},{"title":"skip-django-generic-m2m-field - PyPI","url":"https://pypi.org/project/skip-django-generic-m2m-field/"},{"title":"Generic M2M - Google Groups","url":"https://groups.google.com/g/django-developers/c/Ygcb5xILAvI/m/K0PrmEc_EwAJ"},{"title":"django-generic-notifications - PyPI","url":"https://pypi.org/project/django-generic-notifications/"}]},"Based on the search results, there are a few related PyPI packages for Django generic many-to-many relationships:\n\n## Primary Package: **django-gm2m**\n- **PyPI URL**: https://pypi.org/project/django-gm2m/\n- **Description**: Django generic many-to-many field implementation that exposes a `GM2MField` combining features of the standard Django ManyToManyField\n- **Latest Version**: 0.4 (as shown in results)\n- **GitHub Repository**: https://github.com/coleifer/django-generic-m2m\n- **Purpose**: Allows you to create database-level relationships between various objects using a consistent API\n\n## Alternative Package: **django-generic-m2m-field**\n- **PyPI URL**: https://pypi.org/project/django-generic-m2m-field/\n- **Version**: 0.0.9\n\n## Related Package: **gm2m-relations**\n- **PyPI URL**: https://pypi.org/project/gm2m-relations/\n- **Description**: Implements Django REST Framework serializers to handle generic many-to-many relations\n- **Last Updated**: August 2023\n\nThe most established and commonly referenced package appears to be **django-gm2m** by coleifer, which has been around since at least 2014 and provides the core `GM2MField` implementation for relating any model to any other model in Django, similar to how Generic Foreign Keys work but for many-to-many relationships."],"durationSeconds":7.158644012000004}}
